\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "claim:pv"

\end_inset

 says that for any conditioning 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(Y,\nu\right)$
\end_inset

 on a path space, there is a unique probability 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}^{\nu}$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}^{\nu}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 coincide on all events independent of 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 and the law of 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 under 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}^{\nu}$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $\nu$
\end_inset

.
 
